comment: Meant to use 0.5 oz of the Millenium hops, but accidentally threw in 1 oz.  Hopefully it won't turn out too bitter.
Racked on 8/30/2014.  Final gravity was about 1.015 (measured 1.012 but adding 0.003 for temperature compensation).  Doesn't taste too bad, but will have to wait and see how it is after carbonation.
